---
import Indent from "./Indent.astro";
---

<div
    class="flex flex-col items-center md:flex-row md:justify-between md:gap-x-24"
>
    <div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold">
            Hi there, I'm
            <span
                class="bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-500 to-cyan-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
            >
                LordHamster
            </span> 👋
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-xl leading-9">
            <Indent />This is my little blog site.Welcome,and please have a
            seat. Let me tell you something about me.<br />
            <Indent />I'm a self-taught IT programer,the main code language is
            Python, the second is TypeScript.So I am a full stack programer. And
            now I'm exploring the field of AI.So keep rolling, never settle! <br
            />
            <Indent />Furthermore I'm interested in AIGC、Video Editing、 Voice
            Actor and Drawing.Here are some of my soical accounts.Please have
            fun!
        </p>
        <div class="mt-3 flex gap-3">
            <a
                href="https://space.bilibili.com/13421633?spm_id_from=333.1007.0.0"
                target="_blank"
            >
                <img
                    class="h-11 w-11 hover:translate-y-1"
                    src="/images/bilibili.ico"
                    alt="Bilibili icon"
                    loading="lazy"
                />
            </a>
            <a
                href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCKqdHGEoHpqRdPQD0KYwXoA"
                target="_blank"
            >
                <img
                    class="h-12 w-12 hover:translate-y-1"
                    src="/images/youtube.png"
                    alt="Youtube icon"
                    loading="lazy"
                />
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="shrink-0">
        <img
            class="h-90 w-64"
            src="/images/lordhamster_logo.png"
            alt="Avatar image"
            loading="lazy"
        />
    </div>
</div>
